snippet.title: How Amber Heard Destroyed Her Own Career
snippet.description:
How Amber Heard Destroyed Her Own Career


After being effectively ostracized from Hollywood, Johnny is now getting back on his feet and winning over public opinion.
In the meantime, Amber is losing jobs left and right, and the consensus among fans is that she orchestrated a hoax against Johnny in an attempt to ruin his career.
But it now looks like Amber’s plan is backfiring and instead of ruining Johnny’s career, she’s ruining her own.
